  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: LOCAL PATIENT IDENTIFIER (MOTHER) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_local_patient_identifier__mother_">LOCAL PATIENT IDENTIFIER (MOTHER)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_local_patient_identifier">LOCAL PATIENT IDENTIFIER</xref>
 for the mother.        </p>
      <p>
For the 
              <xref href="https://v3.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/navigation/commissioning_data_sets_menu.html"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_local_patient_identifier__mother_">LOCAL PATIENT IDENTIFIER (MOTHER)</xref>
 uniquely identifies the mother, where the baby's identity is recorded by use of 
              <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_local_patient_identifier">LOCAL PATIENT IDENTIFIER</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
